LiaisonPlugIn, WeatherLiaisonPlugIn
public abstract class SimpleLiaisonPlugIn
extends org.cougaar.core.plugin.SimplePlugIn
implements Liaison

A SimplePlugIn that runs in its own thread and that implements support for liaisons with external agents through the LiaisonManager interface. It also knows how to parse PlugIn parameters that identify it as an agent to external agents.

1.0
